/*
    Process tables for the "happy" test adventure.

    These files cover the seven tables defined by docs/specs_v2.md and
    exercise every condacto in the catalog (except PLAY and PICTURE, which
    would require real media files under SECTION PICTURES).

    Files:
      init.inc.adv      — `_ _:` (runs once at adventure start / restart).
      location.inc.adv  — `<IN|OUT|*> <loc|*>:` (entry / exit hooks).
      turn.inc.adv      — `EVERY n` / `TIMEOUT n` (per main SL).
      item.inc.adv      — `<verb> <item-noun>:` (item-bound interactions).
      npc.inc.adv       — `<verb> <npc-noun>:` (character-bound, includes
                          one example of nested sub-processes for quoted
                          speech `decir elfo "..."`).
      response.inc.adv  — general / fallback table (save, load, quit,
                          restart, syntax fallbacks).
      cron.inc.adv      — clock-driven (`HOURS|MINUTES|SECONDS|AT`).

    Bindings used inside processes: `ITEM`, `NPC`, and the lowercase
    `human` keyword (the player character — `player` label here).

    Author: queru (github.com/queru) 2026
*/

SECTION TABLES

INCLUDE "init.inc.adv"
INCLUDE "location.inc.adv"
INCLUDE "turn.inc.adv"
INCLUDE "item.inc.adv"
INCLUDE "npc.inc.adv"
INCLUDE "response.inc.adv"
INCLUDE "cron.inc.adv"
